{
  "stem": "2833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They build a bank.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They build the stores.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They gave us in the hospital sheets [LAUGHS] on the beds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they put flowers on the park in the middle was made, which was bare until then.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, grass and flowers appeared.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then they had a 5 o'clock band in the afternoon with musicians that were there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And all that was filmed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the Red Cross people were there and saw everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And after the war, they said they didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they felt that they didn't want to do anything to make our life worse.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they accepted whatever they were shown.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then one day, [LAUGHS] after all that was very pretty, Mr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Eichmann came on inspection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I had become a very close friend of Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Edelstein, who was the head of the Jewish ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he asked me to come along because when you walk with him, there always has to be one person opening the door and shouting attention wherever we went.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was very strange because I walked ahead of Edelstein and Eichmann and heard them speak Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then later on, Edelstein explained to me that Eichmann had lived in Israel and spoke fluent Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he, he had fun talking Hebrew with, with Edelstein.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was, it was a strange experience.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, that was the highest ranking SS man that we had ever seen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And his reputation had reached us to, already, that, you know, he's very tough and very hard and very mean and everything else.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
